00:56:50.691 --> 00:56:54.920
one would say for $90 a share,
100 shares.

00:56:54.920 --> 00:57:02.391
Someone's willing to buy 100
shares at $90 and over here you

00:57:02.391 --> 00:57:09.230
would see something like,
someone is willing to sell at

00:57:09.230 --> 00:57:18.039
$92, let's say 200 shares.
There's no trade here, right?

00:57:18.039 --> 00:57:21.888
If somebody is willing to buy
at 90 and someone else is

00:57:21.888 --> 00:57:24.810
willing to buy at $92 there's no
trade.

00:57:24.810 --> 00:57:30.182
Then you'll see other orders;
