and the book was probably hard

00:58:43.604 --> 00:58:46.219
to maintain, but now it's all
automatic.

00:58:46.219 --> 00:58:51.440
Suppose someone comes in with a
buy order for 100 at 90 and a

00:58:51.440 --> 00:58:56.313
sell order for 100 at 90,
so someone's willing to sell at

00:58:56.313 --> 00:59:01.217
